<div class="mth">V_drop = I × R_loop
  R_loop = 2 × L × R_per_unit

V_at_end = V_source − V_drop

Ringer voltage minimum: 40 Vrms at customer
Loop current minimum:  18–23 mA for DTMF dial</div></div>
