<h3>Remote Battery Runtime Estimator</h3>
<div class="eli5"><strong>ELI5:</strong> Remote terminals, SLCs, and outside plant enclosures use small battery banks. This estimates how long the batteries will last at a given load — important for knowing if your site will survive a power outage.
<div class="mth">Simple estimate: T = Ah / I
Peukert (more accurate):
