<!-- Heat Load -->
<div id="m9-heat" class="stab-page">
<div class="grid">
<div class="card">
<h3>CO / Data Room Heat Load Calculator</h3>
<div class="eli5"><strong>ELI5:</strong> Every watt of electrical power consumed by equipment eventually becomes heat in the room. To keep the room cool, you must remove that heat. One ton of cooling = 12,000 BTU/hr = 3.517 kW. Size your cooling to the actual IT load, not the nameplate rating — equipment rarely runs at full nameplate.
<div class="mth">Heat load = Total_IT_power_W × 3.412 BTU/hr per watt
Tons of cooling = Heat_load_BTU / 12,000
kW of cooling = Total_IT_power_W / 1000

PUE (Power Usage Effectiveness):
  PUE = Total_facility_power / IT_equipment_power
  PUE = 1.0 (perfect) → 1.5 (typical CO) → 2.0+ (old facility)</div></div>
<div class="field"><label>Total IT equipment power (W) — sum of all equipment</label><input type="number" id="hl-w" placeholder="e.g. 15000" oninput="calcHL()"></div>
<div class="field"><label>Lighting and misc. overhead (W)</label><input type="number" id="hl-misc" value="500" oninput="calcHL()"></div>
<div class="field"><label>Number of people in room typically</label><input type="number" id="hl-ppl" value="2" oninput="calcHL()"></div>
<div class="field"><label>PUE target (1.0–2.5)</label><input type="number" id="hl-pue" value="1.5" step="0.1" min="1.0" max="3.0" oninput="calcHL()"></div>
<div id="hl-result" class="result"></div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>PUE Calculator</h3>
<div class="eli5"><strong>ELI5:</strong> PUE tells you how efficient your facility is. A PUE of 1.5 means for every 1 kW your servers use, you're consuming 1.5 kW total — 0.5 kW goes to cooling, lighting, UPS losses, etc. Lower is better.</div>
<div class="field"><label>Total facility power (kW) — from utility meter</label><input type="number" id="pue-total" placeholder="e.g. 150" oninput="calcPUE()"></div>
<div class="field"><label>IT equipment power (kW) — PDU readings</label><input type="number" id="pue-it" placeholder="e.g. 100" oninput="calcPUE()"></div>
<div id="pue-result" class="result"></div>
<div class="divider"></div>
<h3>Watts per Rack Density Guide</h3>
