<!-- Arc Flash -->
<div id="m10-arcflash" class="stab-page">
<div class="grid">
<div class="card">
<h3>Arc Flash PPE Category — Quick Assessment</h3>
<div class="eli5"><strong>ELI5:</strong> An arc flash is an explosive release of energy when an electrical fault creates a plasma arc. The incident energy (cal/cm²) determines what PPE you must wear. Higher incident energy = more dangerous = more PPE required.
</div>
<table class="tbl">
