<div id="ior-result" class="result"></div>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>IOR Correction — Wrong IOR Already Used</h3>
<div class="eli5"><strong>If you already took a measurement with the wrong IOR, correct it without re-testing.</strong></div>
<div class="field"><label>Distance shown on OTDR (m or km)</label><input type="number" id="iorc-d" placeholder="e.g. 5034" oninput="calcIORCorr()"></div>
<div class="field"><label>IOR that was set in OTDR</label><input type="number" id="iorc-used" placeholder="e.g. 1.4677" step="0.0001" oninput="calcIORCorr()"></div>
