<tr><td>Frame loss</td><td>% frames lost at each load level</td><td>0% at committed rate</td></tr>
<tr><td>Latency</td><td>One-way or round-trip frame delay</td><td>&lt;1ms metro, &lt;5ms regional</td></tr>
