<h3>JDSU MCT-8000 — Copper Module</h3>
<div class="eli5"><strong>The MCT-8000 (now VIAVI) with its copper module handles T1 DS1 testing, loop qualification, and alarm monitoring. Here's the field workflow for T1 work.</strong></div>
<div class="step"><span class="sn">1</span><span class="stxt"><strong>T1 alarm monitoring:</strong> Connect to the DS1 via bantam jacks (75Ω bridging). Select DS1 Monitor. The MCT displays real-time alarms: LOS, LOF, AIS, RAI, BPV count, ES, SES, UAS. Leave in monitor mode to capture intermittent problems.</span></div>
