<div class="step"><span class="sn">4</span><span class="stxt"><strong>ESF vs D4:</strong> Always verify framing type before testing. D4 (SF) = 12-frame superframe, no CRC. ESF = 24-frame extended superframe with CRC-6 error monitoring. Mismatch shows as continuous LOF. Check with NOC if unsure.</span></div>
