<table class="tbl">
<tr><th>Target</th><th>What to look for</th><th>Common finding</th></tr>
<tr><td>BDFB breakers</td><td>Hot breakers vs neighbors same load</td><td>Failing breaker, overloaded circuit</td></tr>
<tr><td>Bus straps / lug connections</td><td>Hot spots at connection points</td><td>Corroded or loose connections</td></tr>
